{"tid":2453744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中方：會談氣氛不算緊張 尚算順利；美方：屌那媽又Over Run","createTime":"2021-03-19T16:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T17:04:01.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc9ce3a23ad216c489f28588e007c71a48296a5","tid":2453744,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"王毅稱與美首場對話氣氛談不上緊張 第二場還算順利<br />\n<br />\n中美官員預料稍後在美國阿拉斯加，舉行第三場高層戰略對話。<br />\n<br />\n在當地星期四的首場會談上，雙方在開場發言環節充滿火藥味，中美官員亦就開場發言的時間出現爭拗。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒引述國務委員兼外長王毅，在結束首日兩場會談之後說，第一輪會談的氣氛談不上緊張，各自闡述自己立場，第二輪會談還算順利，談了很多地區問題，星期五還有很多問題要談。<br />\n<br />\n亦有美國官員透露，第一場對話實質、認真和直接，會談時間較原本的兩小時長。這名官員又說，按計劃向中方表達美方的利益及優先事項，亦聽了中方的立場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581563-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581563-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=f3e28a38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581563-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e38a54db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581563-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5d4613e36f67ca7ae748eca43c49b09d89ad8cb6","tid":2453744,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T17:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6xon4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6xon4i.png&h=3f097524&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}